    'ts-index' => '1999-04-01.di687',
    'body' => '>At 07:26 PM 4/1/99 +0100, you wrote:
>>On 29 Mar, Joseph R. Dietrich <yikes@evansville.net> wrote:
>>> >>Not actually true as the 40G superdense, space meteorite resistance > >
