J-Drive Fault	3 Faults	Far Gas Giant
	10	Destination Fault	Distance Fault -	1	4D	
Late x1	J-Drive Fault	3 Faults	Far World
	11	Destination Fault	Drive Strain	6	3D	Late 
x2	J-Drive Fault	3 Faults	Far Planetoid
